  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/internet/\" rel=\"tag\">互联网络</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"cn.engadget.com/2013/07/02/google-glass-update-adds-web-viewing/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/07/google-glass-july-update-1372720521.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/GoogleGlass/\">Google Glass</a> Explorer 版推出之后收到过不少更新，但这次的七月更新可说是历来比较重大的一次。它为 Glass 带来了几项新功能，首先包括接听来电或自动读出和回复短讯，只要通过「Ok glass, answer call / read aloud / reply」的语音指令就可以了。用户现在亦能打电话或发短讯给任何 Gmail 联络人。<br />\n<br />\n上次被人发现的<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/05/25/google-glass-delve-shows-hidden-features/\">网页浏览器</a>也是有的，Glass 的用户在搜索一些东西后可以选择以浏览器打开有关网页。至于要怎样浏览呢？很大程度上是通过 Glass 的触摸板，例如在板上以一只手指向上或下滑就可以做出页面滚动的动作、以两只手指向前滑放大页面、将两只手指放在触摸板然后做出头部动作就可以在页面中四周看；而想网页上的东西的话，只需将有关东西放到屏幕的中间，单击触摸板就行了。如无意外，Google Glass 的拥有者将会在几天内收到这个更新。<br />\n<div class=\"postgallery\"><p><strong>Gallery: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/google-glass-july-2013-update-0/\">Google Glass July 2013 update</a></strong></p><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/google-glass-july-2013-update-0/6004803/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/07/screenshot2013-07-01-15-55-18_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/google-glass-july-2013-update-0/6004804/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/07/screenshot2013-07-01-15-56-12_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/google-glass-july-2013-update-0/6004805/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/07/screenshot2013-07-01-15-56-25_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/google-glass-july-2013-update-0/6004806/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/07/screenshot2013-07-01-15-57-27_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/google-glass-july-2013-update-0/6004807/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/07/screenshot2013-07-01-15-57-55_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a></div><br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/07/01/google-glass-update-adds-web-viewing/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"https://plus.google.com/u/0/+projectglass/posts/eV8RUWoodig?cfem=1\">Project Glass（Google+）</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/02/google-glass-update-adds-web-viewing/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20644485/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/02/google-glass-update-adds-web-viewing/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
